{"word":"ὀλιγωρία","slug":"ὀλιγωρία","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<el><b>ὀλιγωρία</b></el> <br/><b><a href='S:Etymology'>Etym.</a> </b>from <el>ὀλῐγωρέω</el>\n<el>(ὀλῐγωρία, ἡ,) </el><p/><div class='li750'><b>1. </b><i>an esteeming lightly, slighting, contempt</i>, <b><a href='S:Herodotus'>Hdt.</a></b>, <b><a href='S:Thucydides'>Thuc.</a></b>, <a href='S:et cetera'>etc.</a><p/></div><div class='li750'><b>2. </b><i>negligence</i>, <a href='S:apud (quoted in)'>ap.</a> <b><a href='S:Demosthenes'>Dem.</a></b><p/></div>"}]}